    <item>
      <title>必和必拓和英美资源集团在南非矿业问题上仍存在分歧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-29/bhp-and-anglo-remain-split-on-south-african-miners</link>
      <description><![CDATA[必和必拓集团 (BHP Group) 以 490 亿美元收购英美资源集团 (Anglo American Plc) 的雄心勃勃计划所剩无几。在周三的最后期限之前，双方仍对必和必拓复杂的交易结构存在分歧。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-29/bhp-and-anglo-remain-split-on-south-african-miners</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 00:41:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国特大城市放宽住房首付和抵押贷款规定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-29/china-s-mega-cities-ease-home-downpayment-mortgage-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上海和深圳等中国大城市已放宽了购房首付和抵押贷款要求。此前，中央政府出台了最有力的房地产行业救助计划，拨出 3000 亿元人民币（410 亿美元）帮助地方政府购买未售出的房屋。Charlie Zhu 在彭博电视台报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-29/china-s-mega-cities-ease-home-downpayment-mortgage-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 00:19:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
