      <title>印度股市上涨取决于莫迪能否赢得 303 个议席</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/modi-needs-to-win-303-plus-seats-to-extend-india-s-stock-market-rally-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博新闻对市场参与者的调查显示，印度股市需要总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的政党在大选中赢得超过 303 个席位，才能延续创纪录的涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/modi-needs-to-win-303-plus-seats-to-extend-india-s-stock-market-rally-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
